Payment Receipt

Dear <%= @customer.name %>,

Thank you for your payment. Your subscription payment has been successfully processed.

Payment Details:
- Subscription: <%= @subscription.reference_number %>
- Plan: <%= @plan.name %>
- Amount: KES <%= @payment.amount %>
- Payment Method: <%= @payment.payment_method.upcase %>
- M-Pesa Transaction ID: <%= @payment.mpesa_transaction_id %>
<% if @payment.mpesa_receipt_number.present? %>
- M-Pesa Receipt: <%= @payment.mpesa_receipt_number %>
<% end %>
- Payment Date: <%= @payment.paid_at.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %>

Subscription Details:
- Current Period: <%= @subscription.current_period_start&.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %> - <%= @subscription.current_period_end&.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %>
- Next Billing Date: <%= @subscription.next_billing_date&.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %>
- Status: <%= @subscription.status.capitalize %>

If you have any questions, please contact our support team.

Thank you for your business!
